trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> (e il relativo valore) di un componente hardware o software di sistema stampa.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"> </xref> classe per la proprietà specificata.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Il `attributeName` devono essere digitati esattamente come il nome di determinate <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "HostingPrintQueue", not "PrintQueue" or "Hostingprintqueue".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A>proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>oggetto deve essere digitato "HostingPrintQueue", non "PrintQueue" o "Hostingprintqueue".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Il nome del <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"> </xref> classe che ha il valore specificato per la proprietà specificata.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Il `attributeName` devono essere digitati esattamente come il nome di determinate <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "HostingPrintQueue", not "PrintQueue" or "Hostingprintqueue".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A>proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>oggetto deve essere digitato "HostingPrintQueue", non "PrintQueue" o "Hostingprintqueue".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Il nome del <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Il valore della proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta il valore della proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that can be cast to a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Un <xref:System.Object>che può essere convertito in un <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>
